Title: A Model of Habituation Applied to Mobile Robots  
Author: Stephen Marsland, Ulrich Nehmzow and Jonathan Shapiro (smarsland, ulrich, 
Date: 26.3.99  
Address: Manchester M13 9PL United Kingdom  
Affiliation: Department of Computer Science University of Manchester  
Abstract: We transfer a neuronal model of the biological phenomenon of habituation, where repeated stimuli begin to be ignored, onto a mobile robot. Results demonstrating the validity of the model are given. Applications of habituation to mobile robots are suggested and areas of further research are presented. 
